          { question: "Should I allow more time from the Left Bank?", answer: "The 6th arrondissement is slightly further from the northern routes than the Right Bank arrondissements. Allow 50 minutes on average, compared to 40-45 from the 1st-4th arrondissements. We recommend 3h15 before a long-haul flight." },
          { question: "Can I book a luxury taxi from Saint-Germain?", answer: "Yes, we offer comfort sedans (Mercedes E-Class or equivalent) at the standard rate. For a premium vehicle or Mercedes V-Class van, the rate is €78. Specify your preference when booking." }
